dict.acceptation: 抵抗，抗拒；忍耐；反对，抵制；

sent.orig: Ash trees can resist many diseases. But they cannot resist ash borer.
sent.trans: 尽管灰树可以抵抗许多疾病，却不能抵挡绿色的钻空虫。

sent.orig: Ash trees can resist many diseases. But they cannot resist the emerald ash borer bark.
sent.trans: 白蜡树可以抵御许多病害，但是不能抵抗花曲柳窄吉丁。

sent.orig: Ash trees can resist many diseases. But they cannot resist the emerald ash borer.
sent.trans: 白腊树能抵抗很多疾病，但它们不能抵抗白腊树绿甲虫。

sent.orig: Therefore whoever resists authority resist what God has appointed and those who resist will incur judgment.
sent.trans: 所以抗拒掌权的，就是抗拒神的命；抗拒的必自取刑罚。

sent.orig: Temptation comes in many forms, often so potent, so animal, that It'seems impossible to resist.
sent.trans: 诱惑万千，强烈、本能得让人无法抵抗。
